1509	Mis-dated old revisions of datasets	dread		"e.g. http://thedatahub.org/dataset/osm%402011-07-12T12%3A16%3A47.590358 gives:
{{{
This is the current revision of this dataset, as edited at 2011-07-12 12:16.
}}}
but it should say the date 2011-07-12 (which is the data being displayed).

The problem is looking at PackageRevision, when it might be a tag or extra."	defect	assigned	minor		ckan				ckan	none
